Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:43.00,DCMain,CONAN,0,0,0,,{\be6}كان ذلك مثاليًا
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:46.53,DCMain,CONAN,0,0,0,,{\be6}عـ-عمي؟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:51.36,DCMain,KOGORO,0,0,0,,{\be6}أنا منهك
